# Vercel Sandbox Authentication
# ================================
# 
# OPTION 1 (Recommended): Use Vercel OIDC Token
# Run `vercel link` and `vercel env pull` to get this automatically
# This is the easiest method for local development
#
# VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN=<auto-generated by vercel env pull>
#
# OPTION 2: Manual Access Token
# Use this if OIDC is unavailable (external CI/CD, non-Vercel environments)
# 
# VERCEL_TOKEN=<your access token from vercel.com/account/settings/tokens>
# VERCEL_TEAM_ID=<your team ID from team settings>
# VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=<your project ID from project settings>

# OpenAI API Key (for Layer 4+)
# ================================
# This will be passed INTO the sandbox for LLM calls
# The agent running inside the sandbox will use this
#
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
